 \"from\": 807, \"to\": 842}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic games\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Paris's show - long, winding, and frequently gravely dull - gave that vast audience a new twist.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 869, \"end\": 874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.536253317922161e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that vast audience\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"a new twist\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a sense of one-upmanship inherent in the Olympic ceremonies, which peaked over the 2008 and 2012 games.\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic ceremonies\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1035}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2008 and 2012 games\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beijing's curtain-raiser - considered one of the greatest theatrical spectacles ever mounted - was a $100m propaganda extravaganza.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the greatest theatrical spectacles\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"a $100m propaganda extravaganza\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was followed, in 2012, by a Danny Boyle-directed schmaltz-fest,Isles of Wonder, within Stratford's Olympic stadium.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stratford-upon-Avon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.148741948976167e-15, \"text\": \"Stratford\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stratford-upon-Avon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stratford-upon-Avon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wonder\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Rio, in 2016, could not match the sheer scale of these performances, and the less said about the damp squib TokyoOlympicsthe better.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999997478471732, \"rank\": 2.5215284859936904e-07, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sheer scale\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"these performances\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"the damp squib\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"TokyoOlympicsthe\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Could Paris restore some pride to proceedings?\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1474, \"end\": 1479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.536253317922161e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some pride\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"proceedings\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thomas Jolly, the actor and theatre director given the reins as artistic director of the ceremony, called tonight's show an opportunity to \\\"illustrate the richness and plurality shaped by [Paris's] history\\\".\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1516, \"end\": 1522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"score\": 0.9999999987012416, \"rank\": 1.0671873238852117e-09, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http: